        <activity xml:id="activity-TI8prule3">
            <introduction>
                <p>
                    Consider if <m>p=1</m> then <m>\frac{1}{x^p}=\frac{1}{x}</m> and <m>\displaystyle \int \frac{1}{x}\ dx=\ln|x|+C</m>.
                </p>
